00:04:10.500 --> 00:04:13.710
I've just been doing more shoots than usual lately.

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.560
Wow...

00:04:16.210 --> 00:04:19.880
You look very different than usual in this, Kitagawa-san.

00:04:19.880 --> 00:04:22.650
Maybe 'cause I've got an actual makeup artist doing my face.

00:04:22.650 --> 00:04:25.570
Why have you been doing more shoots lately?

00:04:25.820 --> 00:04:27.990
Oh, that's because...

00:04:27.990 --> 00:04:29.770
Sparkle, sparkle, sparkle, sparkle!
I want that DSLR camera.

00:04:31.090 --> 00:04:32.370
Mama's gotta get that check.

00:04:33.630 --> 00:04:34.720
Oh...

