Why is this happening to me?!

00:05:27.340 --> 00:05:31.310
N-N-No, stop! Stop!

00:05:41.820 --> 00:05:43.650
Wow, what an ending!
Yoshiko Amasawa

00:05:44.030 --> 00:05:45.320
That was a great movie!

00:05:46.220 --> 00:05:50.150
