God, that was rough. If I had any math to do, I would've died.

00:06:24.370 --> 00:06:25.280
We do, though.

00:06:25.810 --> 00:06:27.940
I already did the drills.

00:06:27.940 --> 00:06:30.280
No way. I don't have any...

00:06:30.280 --> 00:06:34.610
Plonk! And now, for our next question... D'oh...

00:06:33.550 --> 00:06:35.360
Uh, I think...

00:06:36.190 --> 00:06:38.620
I might've left them at school!

00:06:41.200 --> 00:06:43.700
We got in trouble for not coming here in our uniforms.

00:06:43.700 --> 00:06:46.050
I'm super sorry I made you come with me.

00:06:46.250 --> 00:06:48.600
It's fine. It's on my way home, anyway.

00:06:48.600 --> 00:06:50.640
I'm glad you found your math drills.

00:06:50.640 --> 00:06:51.580
Yeah.

00:06:52.530 --> 00:06:56.970
But seriously, the school looks hella creepy after watching that movie.

00:06:56.970 --> 00:06:58.870
Not to mention our footsteps are echoing.

00:06:58.870 --> 00:07:01.980
If we got here any later, we would've been doing a full-on test of courage.

00:07:02.290 --> 00:07:04.610
Yikes... Yes.

00:07:05.040 --> 00:07:08.110
Oh, I need to buy some things to make dinner.

00:07:08.690 --> 00:07:11.430
I know. Would you like to join us for dinner?

00:07:11.430 --> 00:07:12.490
Can I?

00:07:12.490 --> 00:07:14.620
It's been way too long. I can't wait!

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:18.000
I'm pretty sure you've only been eating that fried rice of yours.

00:07:18.700 --> 00:07:20.370
Whatcha makin' tonight?

00:07:20.370 --> 00:07:24.660
I was thinking cold somen noodles with some shrimp, onion, and mitsuba kakiage.

00:07:24.660 --> 00:07:27.170
F'real?! That sounds amazing!

00:07:27.380 --> 00:07:30.950
You can even make kakiage? You've got mad skills, Gojo-kun.

00:07:31.260 --> 00:07:35.220
Fried foods are way too high-level for me.

00:07:40.910 --> 00:07:44.080
I don't have swimming class, so I've never gotten to go in.

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:46.330
It's so huge up close!

00:07:46.330 --> 00:07:49.990
Won't we get in trouble for coming up here when we're not on the swim team?

00:07:50.320 --> 00:07:52.600
I'm sure regular students are allowed up here.

00:07:52.600 --> 00:07:54.450
It looks so nice and cool!

00:07:54.780 --> 00:07:56.300
I'mma dip my foot in.

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:58.320
I really don't think you should!

00:07:58.320 --> 00:07:59.940
No worries. It'll just be for a sec.

00:08:01.320 --> 00:08:02.080
Kitagawa-san!

00:08:10.210 --> 00:08:11.450
Kitagawa-san!

00:08:20.980 --> 00:08:23.780
Dude, I seriously thought I was a goner just now.

00:08:23.780 --> 00:08:27.110
You're telling me! Kitagawa-san, you can't swim?!

00:08:27.860 --> 00:08:30.320
Nope, can't even float.

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:35.700
Didn't you say you went to the beach with your friends around the beginning of the month?

00:08:35.700 --> 00:08:36.990
Did you actually have fun?

00:08:36.990 --> 00:08:38.570
You mean 'cause I can't swim?

00:08:38.570 --> 00:08:39.610
Er, yes.

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:43.540
Hm... I really don't mind.

00:08:43.540 --> 00:08:47.140
I basically go to eat, chat, and take pics,

00:08:47.140 --> 00:08:49.250
so it's plenty fun.

00:08:49.450 --> 00:08:51.370
Oh, I see.

00:08:51.370 --> 00:08:52.750
Y'know...

00:08:53.310 --> 00:08:56.680
I love when I'm sitting on the sand, listening to the waves,

00:08:56.680 --> 00:09:02.350
and watching the ocean get all sparkly from the sun reflecting off it.

00:09:03.030 --> 00:09:06.470
So I always wanna go, even if I can't swim.

00:09:17.290 --> 00:09:21.450
You think I'm a little nuts for loving the ocean so much when I can't swim?

00:09:25.950 --> 00:09:28.060
What? Did I say something that hilarious?

00:09:28.590 --> 00:09:30.890
No, no. I'm sorry.

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:33.980
It's not nuts at all.

00:09:35.670 --> 00:09:37.180
Of course...

00:09:37.680 --> 00:09:39.140
I feel the same.

00:09:39.970 --> 00:09:42.620
Even though I can't paint their faces well yet...

00:09:43.850 --> 00:09:45.840
I absolutely love hina dolls.

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:49.010
Yeah, exactly! That's what I mean.

00:09:49.010 --> 00:09:51.550
I'm pretty sure everyone feels the same way.

00:09:51.550 --> 00:09:52.690
Yes.

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:56.800
But if you drown, you'll die, so please try to avoid that...

00:09:56.800 --> 00:09:59.320
I promise I'll be more careful.

00:10:01.380 --> 00:10:02.360
Gojo-kun.
Yes?

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:07.060
I'm gonna try to find a festival that's still happening,

00:10:07.060 --> 00:10:08.460
so if I do, wanna come with me?

00:10:08.690 --> 00:10:10.660
Huh? What about your homework, though?

00:10:10.660 --> 00:10:12.160
You've still got quite a bit to do.

00:10:12.160 --> 00:10:14.000
Oh, right.

00:10:14.390 --> 00:10:16.860
Uh... I'll finish the rest super fast!

00:10:16.860 --> 00:10:18.670
Just help me with the parts I don't get!

00:10:19.590 --> 00:10:21.350
Sure, of course.

