August I'm actually doing math. Praise me?

00:10:36.610 --> 00:10:40.110
Good job!

00:10:45.880 --> 00:10:49.230
I'm glad to hear Marin-chan managed to finish all her homework.

00:10:49.230 --> 00:10:50.040
Yeah.

00:10:51.050 --> 00:10:52.290
Okay, I'll see you later.

00:10:52.570 --> 00:10:53.490
Yup.

00:10:53.490 --> 00:10:55.110
Watch out for cars.

00:10:56.800 --> 00:11:00.880
Gojo Dolls

00:11:01.190 --> 00:11:03.240
Have a great time!

00:11:21.660 --> 00:11:23.810
There's so many people...

00:11:23.810 --> 00:11:25.310
I had no idea it got this crowded.

00:11:30.250 --> 00:11:32.870
I finished my homework!!!
Now we can go to the festival So Happy
Okay, wanna meet up at the shrine entrance at 6PM?
Sure Oh, man... I'm so friggin' excited!!!

00:11:30.250 --> 00:11:34.150
I'm looking forward to it, too Shrine

00:11:33.700 --> 00:11:37.130
Even meeting up right now might be difficult.
Shrine

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:40.340
I wonder if Kitagawa-san made it okay...

00:11:42.620 --> 00:11:45.360
Yay, I found you!

00:11:47.850 --> 00:11:50.060
Sorry to keep you waiting.

00:11:51.540 --> 00:11:54.550
The crowds here are crazy, so I had a hard time getting through.

00:11:55.540 --> 00:11:57.260
I-It's fine...

00:11:58.430 --> 00:12:00.110
Hey, you're wearing your jinbei!

00:12:00.110 --> 00:12:03.040
I knew it'd look great on you! Noice!

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:06.200
And K-Kitagawa-san, you're wearing a yukata...

00:12:06.940 --> 00:12:07.750
Yup!

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:13.000
I went all out and had someone do my hair and get me into this yukata.

00:12:14.710 --> 00:12:16.160
What's up?

00:12:16.160 --> 00:12:16.960
Huh?!

00:12:17.290 --> 00:12:18.940
Wait, lemme guess...

00:12:18.940 --> 00:12:21.550
You're one of those guys who gets excited from seeing the nape of a girl's neck?

00:12:22.170 --> 00:12:24.890
Yikes Wait, seriously?

00:12:25.340 --> 00:12:34.060
U-Um... I-I wouldn't say... uh... Glance Blush

00:12:32.110 --> 00:12:34.060
For real?!

00:12:34.300 --> 00:12:39.440
For real? For real, for real, for real, for real, for real?!
W-Well, Japanese clothes are really nice.

00:12:39.690 --> 00:12:46.070
Badump Badump Badump Badump Badump Badump

00:12:41.060 --> 00:12:42.910
I'm so hyped right now!

00:12:42.910 --> 00:12:45.700
I'm so glad I wore a yukata!

00:12:46.070 --> 00:12:48.580
Beef Skewers Takoyaki
I'm deffo gonna be showing off the nape of my neck!

00:12:50.690 --> 00:12:53.700
Wh-What time do the fireworks start?

00:12:53.960 --> 00:12:54.650
Seven!

00:12:54.650 --> 00:12:56.790
You were that excited about this?!

