Huh?

00:13:13.100 --> 00:13:14.640
Okonomiyaki Thanks!

00:13:15.060 --> 00:13:17.540
This looks great, Kitagawa-san—

00:13:17.350 --> 00:13:19.420
Gone Huh?!

