Delicious Yakitori They have yakitori, too!

00:13:21.280 --> 00:13:22.650
Step right up!

00:13:23.220 --> 00:13:26.070
Right... I wonder how many I should get...

00:13:24.370 --> 00:13:26.070
Th-This is, uh...

00:13:26.700 --> 00:13:27.610
Grilled Squid Beef Steak Skewers Yum
Chicken Skin Gyoza Fried Chicken Okonomiyaki

00:13:28.240 --> 00:13:28.870
Cotton Candy Chocolate Bananas Cotton Candy Shaved Ice

00:13:35.360 --> 00:13:37.240
You bought so much...

00:13:38.890 --> 00:13:40.960
I mean, that's pretty normal for two people, isn't it?

00:13:42.280 --> 00:13:44.360
Let's go sit at the plaza and eat!

00:13:44.360 --> 00:13:45.670
Thank you for waiting.

00:13:46.260 --> 00:13:50.600
The fireworks show will start momentarily.

00:13:50.600 --> 00:13:52.810
Shoot, let's hurry, Gojo-kun.

00:13:52.810 --> 00:13:53.890
Right.

00:13:55.280 --> 00:13:58.920
This is my first time coming down to the plaza to actually watch the fireworks.

00:13:58.920 --> 00:14:00.440
Wow, really?

00:14:01.060 --> 00:14:03.780
You've never gone to the fireworks festival at Iwatsuki?

00:14:04.080 --> 00:14:07.240
That's sort of a waste when you live so close, isn't it?

00:14:53.010 --> 00:14:56.110
I can smell the gunpowder and smoke...

00:14:56.890 --> 00:14:58.290
People cheering...

00:14:59.470 --> 00:15:00.840
Seeing them so up close...

00:15:01.800 --> 00:15:04.500
The sound resonates through your whole body.

00:15:11.320 --> 00:15:15.010
Last year, the year before, and even before that...

00:15:16.100 --> 00:15:19.100
Every year, I'd be alone in my room...

00:15:20.540 --> 00:15:24.770
Fireworks were just some loud, echoing noise I'd hear off in the distance.

00:15:31.820 --> 00:15:33.500
And yet, this year...

00:16:16.440 --> 00:16:17.130
Nyah.

00:16:17.410 --> 00:16:19.440
Oh, God! Your tongue!

00:16:20.150 --> 00:16:22.160
Do you know what's happened to it?!

00:16:22.160 --> 00:16:25.260
It instantly turns into an cool color when you eat Blue Hawaii.

00:16:25.260 --> 00:16:26.640
And you still chose to eat it?!

00:16:26.640 --> 00:16:27.460
Yup!

00:16:28.080 --> 00:16:29.260
Nyah! Nyah! Nyah!
That's enough already!

00:16:33.080 --> 00:16:36.010
Ow... Wow...

00:16:36.270 --> 00:16:38.150
The straps really did a number on your feet.

00:16:38.150 --> 00:16:40.470
It must hurt to walk.

00:16:41.440 --> 00:16:44.380
There's a convenience store nearby, so I'll buy some bandages.

00:16:44.380 --> 00:16:45.310
It's fine.

00:16:45.310 --> 00:16:47.520
It'd be a pain for you to have to go and come back.

00:16:47.520 --> 00:16:51.120
But... Just take me with you.

00:16:51.780 --> 00:16:52.950
Take you with me?

00:16:53.730 --> 00:16:56.450
We're so high up!

00:16:56.450 --> 00:17:00.180
I envy you! You get to see everything from all the way up here.

00:17:00.180 --> 00:17:02.910
Sh-She smells so nice...

00:17:03.230 --> 00:17:05.420
Gojo-kun! How tall are you?

00:17:05.420 --> 00:17:07.760
A-A hundred and eighty....

00:17:08.210 --> 00:17:10.510
Kitagawa-san! It's dangerous if you move too much!

00:17:10.510 --> 00:17:12.010
Whoops, my bad.

00:17:12.010 --> 00:17:14.720
Wow, I figured you were about that tall.

00:17:16.260 --> 00:17:19.200
The last part of the fireworks was insane.

00:17:19.200 --> 00:17:20.720
They were very beautiful.

00:17:21.100 --> 00:17:23.540
It's kinda hilarious that you can't see them well, from all the smoke.

00:17:23.540 --> 00:17:25.550
I never knew it'd end up like that.

00:17:26.980 --> 00:17:28.900
I'm really glad I came.

00:17:29.370 --> 00:17:32.690
Me, too! Or, well...

00:17:32.960 --> 00:17:37.030
It kinda sucks that this happened at the end.

00:17:37.300 --> 00:17:39.650
You're not used to wearing them, so it happens.

00:17:40.490 --> 00:17:41.630
But, y'know,

00:17:41.630 --> 00:17:44.640
when this kinda crap happens, it doesn't matter how much fun you were having.

00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:46.830
Things get sorta "meh," right?

00:17:47.800 --> 00:17:49.600
Sorry about this, Gojo-kun.

00:17:53.150 --> 00:17:55.730
I promise I'll be more careful next year.

00:18:02.560 --> 00:18:03.740
Next year, too?

00:18:05.370 --> 00:18:08.650
Next year, let's go to Iwatsuki's fireworks festival, too.

00:18:08.650 --> 00:18:10.130
Yes, let's go.

00:18:10.130 --> 00:18:14.420
Actually, why don't we just hit up all the fireworks festivals in the Kanto region?

00:18:14.420 --> 00:18:16.510
Really? Do you think we can actually do it?

00:18:16.510 --> 00:18:18.450
Anything is possible if you try.

00:18:18.450 --> 00:18:19.780
Not that I'd know.

00:19:57.380 --> 00:19:59.520
I guess I'll call it a night.

00:20:05.930 --> 00:20:08.200
Kitagawa-san? Is everything okay?

00:20:08.960 --> 00:20:12.080
Gojo-kun... What were you doing right now?

00:20:12.080 --> 00:20:13.810
I was about to go to bed.

00:20:13.810 --> 00:20:16.510
It's pretty late. Did something happen?

00:20:16.510 --> 00:20:20.080
Well... Not exactly...

00:20:21.210 --> 00:20:25.010
I-I just wanted to hear your voice...

00:20:27.090 --> 00:20:29.950
I'm way too scared to sleep right now!

